description:
Now that the new LEGO Marvel character busts have been released, it's time to assemble! Sit back and enjoy this long, relaxing build featuring the Iron Man MK4 armor and the Iron Spider-Man suit. These build-and-display models accurately recreate both characters from the Marvel Cinematic Universe, capturing key details and dynamic articulation for increased display options. If you’re ASMR sensitive, you may feel your Spidey sense tingling!

author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
Today on the podcast, we take a peek at the exciting premiere of Marvel Studios’ The Fantastic Four: First Steps as we hear from Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby, Ebon Moss-Bachrach, and Joseph Quinn from the red carpet. Plus, we spotlight Senior Paralegal for Marvel Studios’ Legal and Business Affairs, Matt Gilbert. And finally, we get the latest from Magic: The Gathering’s Max McCall, Sarah Wassell, Mark Rosewater, and Jadine Klomparens as they share the behind-the-scenes creation of the Magic: The Gathering | Marvel’s Spider-Man set (14:33). All time codes are approximate.

00:00 - Welcome Back! 
1:10 - Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby, Ebon Moss-Bachrach, and Joseph Quinn talk F4
7:01 - Spotlight: Senior Paralegal for Marvel Studios’ Legal and Business Affairs Matt Gilbert 
14:33 - Max McCall, Sarah Wassell, Mark Rosewater, and Jadine Klomparens on BTS for Magic: The Gathering | Marvel’s Spider-Man
